@startuml
title 裝飾模式 (Decorator Pattern) - 星巴克咖啡系統

' --- 樣式設定 ---
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
skinparam monochrome false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle

skinparam class {
BackgroundColor White
ArrowColor #2ecc71
BorderColor #27ae60
}

' --- 核心組件 (Component) ---
abstract class Beverage {
# description: String = "Unknown Beverage"
+ getDescription(): String
+ {abstract} cost(): double
}

' --- 裝飾者基類 (Decorator) ---
abstract class CondimentDecorator extends Beverage {
# beverage: Beverage
+ {abstract} getDescription(): String
}

' --- 具體組件 (Concrete Components) ---
package "咖啡基底 (Coffee Bases)" {
class Espresso extends Beverage {
+ Espresso()
+ cost(): double
}

class HouseBlend extends Beverage {
    + HouseBlend()
    + cost(): double
}

class DarkRoast extends Beverage {
    + DarkRoast()
    + cost(): double
}

class Decaf extends Beverage {
    + Decaf()
    + cost(): double
}


}

' --- 具體裝飾者 (Concrete Decorators) ---
package "調味品裝飾 (Condiments)" {
class Mocha extends CondimentDecorator {
+ Mocha(beverage: Beverage)
+ getDescription(): String
+ cost(): double
}

class Milk extends CondimentDecorator {
    + Milk(beverage: Beverage)
    + getDescription(): String
    + cost(): double
}

class Soy extends CondimentDecorator {
    + Soy(beverage: Beverage)
    + getDescription(): String
    + cost(): double
}

class Whip extends CondimentDecorator {
    + Whip(beverage: Beverage)
    + getDescription(): String
    + cost(): double
}


}

' --- 關係連線 ---
CondimentDecorator o-- Beverage : 組合 (包裹一個 Beverage 物件)

note top of Beverage : 抽象組件：\n定義了咖啡的描述與計算金額的介面。
note bottom of CondimentDecorator : 裝飾者基類：\n必須與被裝飾物件屬於同一類型，\n且持有一個該類型的引用。
note right of Mocha : 具體裝飾者：\n在原有 cost() 之上疊加自己的價格，\n並在 getDescription() 附加說明。

@enduml